    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="EV3《蝙蝠》"><a href="#EV3《蝙蝠》" class="headerlink" title="EV3《蝙蝠》"></a>EV3《蝙蝠》</h1><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/vesperusX/image/blog-imageIMG_20260411_233247.jpeg" alt="IMG_20260411_233247"></p>
